# frequency

**Instance Property**

The frequency tested in the hearing test.

## Declaration

```swift
@NSCopying var frequency: HKQuantity { get }
```

## Discussion

This object uses [doc://com.apple.healthkit/documentation/HealthKit/HKUnit/hertz()] units.

## Accessing Data

- **leftEarSensitivity**: The sensitivity of the left ear.
- **rightEarSensitivity**: The sensitivity of the right ear.
